Transforming GOVERNANCE with Michel Bauwens: Rethinking Civilization from the Ground Up. Commons, Collapse, and the Rise of Translocal Futures. In conversation wth Carola Verschoor.

"In this episode, we explore how the commons, Web3, and translocal networks are reshaping civilization, governance, and value creation. Michel Bauwens shares visionary insights into post-capitalist futures, techno-ethical frameworks, and how seed forms of change are already emerging in today’s world."

